data.description: Own almost an acre on a private corner lot with territorial views in the heart of Northwood! All updated with a new roof, new flooring, new carpets, paint in & out, fenced backyard and a freshened up driveway. Maintenance free decking. Enjoy the views and your morning coffee on the country front porch! This 2-story home is bright and cheery with 4 beds, 3 baths. 2 car garage, plus extra parking.
